desc:
Compuscan has picked up a difference in the amounts of Commercial records that they are receiving. Below figures reflect a large difference. Black volume is Lightstone and Red is what Compuscan say they have received in the raw file before processing.

Jul: 3208           - 2018
Aug: 3507         - 2142
Sep: 2789         - 1731
Oct: 2569          - 1780
Nov: 2118         - 1332

Please would you investigate and advise why the volumes are so different. There is possibility that we can make more money if there is an issue and it is rectified.
name: CW - CCW251 - Compuscan commercial records discrepancy
